{
  "name": "w06_e09_03.ks",
  "lines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "line": "大急ぎで後片付けをして、朝食もままならないまま\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "line": "家を出てから——\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "line": "俺と絵麻は、なんとか朝の会員勧誘時間に間に合った。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "line": "「お菓子作り同好会です、よろしくお願いします」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051493\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "line": "「よ、よろしく、お願いします」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "line": "登校してくる、ぴかぴかの制服を着ている１年生たちに\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "line": "チラシを手渡していく。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "line": "絵麻はまだぎこちないが、初日と比べるとだいぶマシに……\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "line": "いや、去年までと比べたら、劇的に変わっていた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051494\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "line": "「よろしくお願いします」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "line": "@Talk name=新入生Ａ voice=NP240001\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "line": "「わあ、お菓子作り、私趣味なんですっ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "line": "@Talk name=新入生Ｂ voice=NP250001\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "line": "「へえ、そうなんだぁ……あの、すみません、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "line": "　体験入部とかってできるんですか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051495\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "line": "「い、いま、調理実習室のスペースを借りてる、ので……\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "line": "　そこで申し込みをして、ください……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "line": "@Talk name=新入生Ｂ voice=NP250002\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 67,
      "line": "「分かりました、ありがとうございますっ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 71,
      "line": "新入生の女の子二人が、たたたっと校舎の方へ駆けて行く。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 76,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 77,
      "line": "「すごいじゃないか絵麻、ちゃんと説明できたな」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 80,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051496\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 81,
      "line": "「はい、お兄ちゃん……すごく、どきどきしました……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 84,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 85,
      "line": "絵麻は緊張でぎこちなくなりながらも、微笑を浮かべた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 88,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89,
      "line": "「よし、俺も頑張らないとな」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 92,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 93,
      "line": "予鈴が鳴るまで時間もないことだし、今、手に持っている\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 94,
      "line": "チラシ分くらいは、兄のプライドをかけて配りきらない\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 95,
      "line": "とな。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 99,
      "line": "@Talk name=男性客Ｂ/新入生Ｃ voice=NP270008\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 100,
      "line": "「あのー、すみません」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 105,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051497\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 106,
      "line": "「はい？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 109,
      "line": "@Talk name=男性客Ｂ/新入生Ｃ voice=NP270009\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 110,
      "line": "「俺もお菓子作りに興味があるんですけど……っていうか、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 111,
      "line": "　先輩に興味があるんですけど」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 119,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 120,
      "line": "「なっ……！？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 123,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124,
      "line": "聞き捨てならない言葉に、俺ははっと絵麻の方を見る。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 130,
      "line": "背丈だけは立派な、ひょろっとした新入生が、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 131,
      "line": "絵麻の前に立っていた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 136,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051498\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 137,
      "line": "「………………」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 140,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141,
      "line": "絵麻はチラシの上部を、無言でトントンと叩いて見せる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 144,
      "line": "@Talk name=男性客Ｂ/新入生Ｃ voice=NP270010\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 145,
      "line": "「えっ……女子会員募集中？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 148,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051499\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 149,
      "line": "「ん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 154,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155,
      "line": "絵麻はそっけなく頷くと、配る場所を移動した。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 158,
      "line": "@Talk name=男性客Ｂ/新入生Ｃ voice=NP270011\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 159,
      "line": "「え、あ、ちょっと……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 162,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 163,
      "line": "「今の時間は、こっちが勧誘する側だからな？\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 164,
      "line": "　ナンパはよそでやってくれ、新入生」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 169,
      "line": "@Talk name=男性客Ｂ/新入生Ｃ voice=NP270012\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 170,
      "line": "「ひっ！？　す、すみませんっ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 173,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 174,
      "line": "少し語気を強めると、絵麻に追いすがろうとしていた\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 175,
      "line": "男子生徒は慌てたように逃げていった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 178,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051500\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 179,
      "line": "「ありがとうございます、お兄ちゃん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 182,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 183,
      "line": "「いや……それより、絵麻」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 187,
      "line": "「女子会員募集って、わざわざ限定しているのはどうして\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 188,
      "line": "　なんだ？　いまは一人でも多く会員が欲しいはずだろう」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 191,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 192,
      "line": "俺としてはありがたいことこの上無いのだが、絵麻たちに\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 193,
      "line": "とってメリットがあるとは思えなかった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 198,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051501\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 199,
      "line": "「お菓子作り同好会の男子枠は、もう埋まっています」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 202,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 203,
      "line": "「男子枠？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 208,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051502\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 209,
      "line": "「はい、永久欠番です。結成の理由、ですから」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 212,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 213,
      "line": "「……なるほど」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 216,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 217,
      "line": "同好会を作った最初の理由は、学校に俺と弥恵と絵麻の\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 218,
      "line": "三人が一緒にいられる場所を作るためだった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 221,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 222,
      "line": "弥恵と絵麻が所属している今、欠けているのは——\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 228,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051503\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 229,
      "line": "「んぅ、お姉ちゃんから電話です」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 232,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 233,
      "line": "絵麻は呟き、俺を手招きした。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 242,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE050165\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 243,
      "line": "「あっ、もしもし、絵麻ちゃん？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 247,
      "line": "絵麻がスピーカーモードにしてくれたらしく、俺にも\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 248,
      "line": "弥恵の声が聞こえてきた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 251,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051504\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 252,
      "line": "「はい、どうしました、お姉ちゃん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 258,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE050166\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 259,
      "line": "「さっきね、１年生の女の子が二人来たの」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 262,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263,
      "line": "俺と絵麻は顔を見合わせ、先ほどの女生徒たちだろうと\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264,
      "line": "頷き合った。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 270,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE050167\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 271,
      "line": "「最初は体験入部を希望してたんだけどね、おみやげ用の\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 272,
      "line": "　お菓子を渡したら……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 278,
      "line": "@Talk name=静子 voice=SZ050016\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 279,
      "line": "「こんなにおいしいお菓子が作れるならぜひ入りたいって、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 280,
      "line": "　さっき入会届けを出してくれたのよ〜！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 286,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE050168\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 287,
      "line": "「はわわっ、お、岡野先生」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 290,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 291,
      "line": "浮かれ声の岡野先生が割り込んできて、電話口で感動の\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 292,
      "line": "吐息を何度も漏らしている。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 297,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051505\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 298,
      "line": "「ふぁ……それじゃあ、同好会は、存続、ですね」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 301,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 302,
      "line": "絵麻がかみしめるように呟く。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 308,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE050169\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 309,
      "line": "「うん、それに……絵麻ちゃんの目標の、部活動昇格も、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 310,
      "line": "　あと一人だよ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 315,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051506\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 316,
      "line": "「……っ！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 319,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 320,
      "line": "絵麻は目を見開いた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 323,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 324,
      "line": "口元が、ふにゃ、と緩み始める。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 330,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE050170\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 331,
      "line": "「あっ……また説明希望の子が来たから、切るね」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 334,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051507\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 335,
      "line": "「はい、ではまたあとで……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 341,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 342,
      "line": "通話を終えると、絵麻は俺の顔を見て、瞳をきらきら\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 343,
      "line": "させた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 346,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051508\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 347,
      "line": "「お兄ちゃん……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 352,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 353,
      "line": "「すごいじゃないか、絵麻！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 356,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051509\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 357,
      "line": "「で、でも、決め手はお姉ちゃんのお菓子です」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 360,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 361,
      "line": "「絵麻がチラシを配らなかったら、二人ともお菓子作り\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 362,
      "line": "　同好会の存在すら知らなかったかもしれないだろう」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 365,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051510\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 366,
      "line": "「あ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 369,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 370,
      "line": "俺はおもむろに、手を動かす。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 373,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 374,
      "line": "頭を撫でられると予想したのだろう、絵麻が目を細めて、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 375,
      "line": "少し頭をこちらへ傾ける。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 378,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 379,
      "line": "……が、俺は動かした手をポケットへと入れた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 382,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051511\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 383,
      "line": "「お兄ちゃん……？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 386,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 387,
      "line": "絵麻は不思議そうに首を傾げる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 390,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 391,
      "line": "「前祝いだ、絵麻」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 394,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 395,
      "line": "ポケットから取り出した封筒を、絵麻に差し出す。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 401,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051512\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 402,
      "line": "「えっ……これ……『入部届』……？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 405,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 406,
      "line": "絵麻は慌てたように、ごそごそと封筒を開ける。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 409,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051513\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 410,
      "line": "「お、お兄ちゃんの名前が書いてある……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 415,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051514\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 416,
      "line": "「これ、ど、どうして、お兄ちゃん？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 419,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 420,
      "line": "「前に約束してただろう？　『部活動に昇格したら』、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 421,
      "line": "　いちばん近くで褒めてやるって」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 424,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051515\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 425,
      "line": "「あ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 437,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051516\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 438,
      "line": "『ご褒美に、えまのこと、たくさん、ほめてほしい』\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 441,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 442,
      "line": "『褒める？　そりゃ褒めるけど……それだけでいいのか？』\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 448,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051517\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 449,
      "line": "『うん、いちばんちかくで、大好きなお兄ちゃんが\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 450,
      "line": "　ほめてくれたら、それだけでいい』\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 458,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 459,
      "line": "俺の入部届けを握りしめた絵麻の瞳に、驚きが広がって\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 460,
      "line": "いく。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 463,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 464,
      "line": "それが臨界点を突破すると、絵麻はふにゃりと泣き笑いの\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 465,
      "line": "ような表情になった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 468,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051518\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 469,
      "line": "「部活動になるまでには、あと一人……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 472,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 473,
      "line": "「だから言っただろう、前祝いだって」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 478,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051519\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 479,
      "line": "「あっ……はぅぅ……っ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 482,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 483,
      "line": "今度こそ絵麻の頭を撫でる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 486,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 487,
      "line": "「絵麻が頑張ってもう一人メンバーを集めて、部活動に\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 488,
      "line": "　昇格したその時に……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 491,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 492,
      "line": "「『お菓子作り部』として、俺を部員に加えてくれ。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 493,
      "line": "　だから『入部届』なんだ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 496,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 497,
      "line": "絵麻は、ガラス玉のように大きな瞳で俺を見上げ続け——\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 502,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051520\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 503,
      "line": "「お兄ちゃん、大好きですっ！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 506,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 507,
      "line": "たまらなくなったように抱きついて来た。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 510,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051521\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 511,
      "line": "「うれしい、とってもうれしい……えま、がんばるっ、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 512,
      "line": "　お兄ちゃんに、絶対に部員になってもらう……っ！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 515,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 516,
      "line": "「今の絵麻ならきっと大丈夫だよ……期待してる」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 519,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051522\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 520,
      "line": "「うんっ……うんっ……、お兄ちゃんっ！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 523,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051523\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 524,
      "line": "「大好き、大好き、大好きっ……！　えま、お兄ちゃんの\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 525,
      "line": "　ことがだいすきっ……！」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 530,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 531,
      "line": "周囲の生徒たちの視線もなんのその。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 534,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 535,
      "line": "絵麻は、未だかつて出したことがないほどの大声で、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 536,
      "line": "俺に告白を繰り返す。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 539,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 540,
      "line": "「ああ、絵麻……俺もだよ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 543,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 544,
      "line": "前祝いと、彼女への恋心と、もちろん妹への愛情を\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 545,
      "line": "たっぷり織り交ぜて、俺も絵麻を抱き締め返した。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 548,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051524\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 549,
      "line": "「くすっ……ほめ方、考えておいてね、お兄ちゃん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 552,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 553,
      "line": "「ほめ方？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 556,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051525\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 557,
      "line": "「例えば、今朝みたいに、激しく……たくさん褒めて\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 558,
      "line": "　くれる？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 561,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 562,
      "line": "絵麻がいたずらっぽく微笑む。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 565,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 566,
      "line": "「ま……まずは、頭を撫でさせてもらおうかな」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 569,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051526\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 570,
      "line": "「うん、お兄ちゃん。えま、お兄ちゃんになでられるの、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 571,
      "line": "　大好きだよ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 574,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 575,
      "line": "くるくると表情が変わる絵麻は、女の子としてますます\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 576,
      "line": "魅力的になった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 579,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 580,
      "line": "そんな年下の彼女になら、こうしていたずらっぽく\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 581,
      "line": "からかわれるのも悪くない。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 586,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051527\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 587,
      "line": "「くすくすっ……お兄ちゃん……えま、がんばるよ。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 588,
      "line": "　お兄ちゃんにほめてもらえるように、たくさん\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 589,
      "line": "　がんばるから……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 592,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻 voice=EM051528\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 593,
      "line": "「えまのこと、たくさんなでなでしてね、お兄ちゃん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 596,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 597,
      "line": "光を浴びたガラス玉のように、さまざまに変化する絵麻の\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 598,
      "line": "表情を見つめつつ……\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 601,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 602,
      "line": "俺は、彼女の小さな身体をますます強く抱き締めた。\r\n"
    }
  ]
}